RESOURCE		VERB	ACTION

/cause			GET	Show causes
/cause			POST	Create cause
/cause/:cause_id	GET	Show cause page
/cause/:cause_id	PUT	Edit cause
/cause/:cause_id	DELETE	Delete cause

/user			GET	Show list of users
/user			POST	Register a user
/user/:user_id		GET	Show specific user
/user/:user_id		PUT	Edit specific user
/user/:user_id		DELETE	Delete user


RESOURCE				VERB	ACTION

/cause/:cause_id/user/:user_id		POST	Register user to a cause
